    "home.email.placeholder": "Nhap dia chi email cua ban",
    "home.email.subtitle": "Nhan cau hoi luyen tap hang tuan voi ly giai chi tiet, the on tap duoc ly va chien luoc thi. Viet boi cac nha giao duc dieu duong. Huu ich tu ngay dau tien. Huy dang ky bat ky luc nao.",
    "home.email.title": "Cau hoi ly luan lam sang mien phi duoc gui hang tuan",
    "home.exams.desc": "Bai thi thuc hanh co tinh gio voi giai thich chi tiet va cham diem.",
    "home.exams.title": "Thi thu",
    "home.faq.a1": "Khong. NurseNest la mot nen tang giao duc doc lap. Khong lien ket, khong duoc chung thuc hoac ket noi voi NCLEX, NCSBN, CNO hoac bat ky co quan quan ly dieu duong nao.",
    "home.faq.a10": "Co. Tat ca noi dung NurseNest duoc phat trien va xem xet boi cac chuyen gia dieu duong co kinh nghiem lam sang va giao duc.",
    "home.faq.a2": "Cac cau hoi cua NurseNest duoc thiet ke de phan anh ly luan lam sang va cac mo hinh nhan thuc duoc kiem tra trong ky thi cap phep.",
    "home.faq.a3": "Hoan toan co the. Nhieu sinh vien dieu duong su dung NurseNest song song voi cac khoa hoc de cung co sinh ly benh, duoc ly va ky nang ly luan lam sang.",
    "home.faq.a4": "Ngan hang cau hoi truyen thong cho ban mot cau hoi, bon lua chon va dap an dung. NurseNest cung cap giai thich sau sac ve ly do dap an dung chinh xac va ly do moi phuong an nhieu sai.",
    "home.faq.a5": "Co. NurseNest ho tro chuan bi thi cho tat ca cac ky thi cap phep chinh, bao gom NCLEX-RN, NCLEX-PN, REX-PN va cac ky thi chung chi NP.",
    "home.faq.a6": "Goi mien phi bao gom cac module nen tang tien dieu duong, so do giai phau va sinh ly tuong tac, giai thich ro rang lam sang va toi da 50 the ghi nho.",
    "home.faq.a6b": "Che do Hoc su dung lap lai gian cach de giup ban lam chu moi the. Che do Kiem tra la bai danh gia co gio voi bao cao chi tiet o cuoi.",
    "home.faq.a7": "Co. Tat ca dang ky co the duoc huy bat ky luc nao thong qua trang ho so cua ban. Ban van co quyen truy cap cac tinh nang cao cap cho den cuoi ky thanh toan.",
    "home.faq.a8": "Co. NurseNest bao gom cac dinh dang cau hoi duoc thiet ke de phan anh cac mo hinh nhan thuc duoc kiem tra trong ky thi the he moi, bao gom cac nghien cuu tinh huong va kich ban phan doan lam sang.",
    "home.faq.a9prefix": "NurseNest cung cap hon",
    "home.faq.a9suffix": "cau hoi luyen tap bao quat tat ca cac linh vuc noi dung dieu duong chinh. Cau hoi moi duoc them moi tuan.",
