    "home.qbank.desc": "Loc theo cap do, he thong co the hoac chu de. Moi cau hoi bao gom giai thich chi tiet ve ly do dap an dung la chinh xac va tai sao moi phuong an nhieu la sai. Cau hoi moi duoc them hang tuan.",
    "home.qbank.title": "Cau hoi luyen tap",
